1.how to run:
Use make to make all the files needed in this project.
Or else, use 'make client' to generate the client execution file,
and use 'make server' to generate the server execution file.
Running the files with the spec's asking.

2.What I do:
client:
receive/send message from/to multiple server
support -n -t command
print out accorfing to P.9
translate host name into IP
server:
receive/send message from/to multiple client
print output according to P.11
